description: From the manufacturer Green Toys Watering Can Perfect for the garden & fun at the beach Perfect for the garden, and also fun at the beach, the Green Toys Watering Can is a classic set that encourages kids to help take care of the world around them. Made in the USA from recycled plastic milk jugs, it features an easy-to-pour spout and cotton rope carrying handle that make this set frustration-free for little gardeners. It's great for spending time together outside, and kids will love helping and playing alongside the grownups to watch their garden grow. And it's even fun in the bath! Made safe in the USA with recycled plastic milk jugs Manufactured and assembled in the USA, it’s made from recycled plastic milk jugs (HDPE #2 plastic) that save energy and reduce greenhouse gas emissions. With no external coatings, paints, or dyes, this super-safe, durable toy is good for the earth and safe and fun for little ones. It’s also packaged in recycled and recyclable materials with no plastic films or twist ties, and printed with soy ink. Classic toys made with play The Watering Can is manufactured in the USA with a tight, local supply chain that minimises transportation emissions and supports the domestic economy. Perfect in a sandbox, toy box, or gift box, it's ideal for little hands. Specifically designed for easy pouring with a rope handle. Dishwasher safe, it's great for indoor and outdoor play since it won't rust and is easy to clean! At a glance: Age 18+ months Ready to play indoors or out Made in the USA from recycled milk jugs Sturdy, well-designed and loaded with Good Green Fun Phthalate and BPA free Easy to clean - dishwasher safe
